      <title>阿根廷米雷加速电锯和搅拌机打击财政赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/argentinas-milei-revs-up-chainsaw-blender-fiscal-deficit-attack-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷自由主义总统哈维尔·米莱正在加紧打击该国严重的财政赤字，加倍实施“电锯式”支出削减和“混合式”紧缩政策，挤压购买力，他希望能降低猖獗的通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/argentinas-milei-revs-up-chainsaw-blender-fiscal-deficit-attack-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 17:31:26 GMT</pubDate>
